              Electric Vehicle (EV) System Warranty Coverage
            </strong>
            <em>
              Ends Mar 10, 2018 or 100,000 mile (whichever comes first)
            </em>
            <p>
              EV System Warranty covers fir 120 months or 100,000 miles. Items covered by the EV System Warranty include the following EV System components: Electric Motorr, Gear Drive Unit, Battery pack (“EV Battery”), Electric Power Control Unit (EPCU), On Board Charger (OBC), and all internal part. The EV System Warranty does not cover any other elctrical components in the vehicle, such as (but not limited to) the traditional 12 volt car battery, alternator, or other starter components.
            </p>
            <strong>
              Limited Powertrain Warranty Coverage 
              <span class="tooltip-i">
                <i
                data-toggle="tooltip"
                data-placement="bottom"
